flowchart TD
    Start([Start application]) --> Init[AppContent.initContent()]
    Init --> Backend[Create SpaceShooterBackend]
    Backend --> World[Initialize GameWorld]
    World --> Managers[Setup CollisionManager, SpawnManager, DifficultyManager]
    Managers --> UiPort[Ui.setUiPorts() registers SpaceShooterUiPort]
    UiPort --> Window[Create and show main game window]
    Window --> Ready[Game ready to start]
